This is Ninponix Visual Document Editor which is based on the NLPP (Ninponix Live Preview Protocol). Everytime you start Ninponix Visual Document Editor, Ninponix Office will show you these tips which can be disabled by unchecking the checkbox saying "Show tips at startup". Click "Next" to see the next tip / get started with Ninponix Visual Document Editor.
